            <h3>Remake Our World</h3>
            <br>
            <p>Remake is a global advocacy organization that is fighting for fair pay and climate justice in the clothing industry. They aim to end poverty wages, unsafe working conditions, and gender-based violence in the garment industry. They primarily approach sustainable and ethical fashion through the lens of workers rights and believe that by paying garment workers a living wage, we can begin to reduce the social and environmental harm caused by the fashion industry. Some key campaigns include #PayUp, #VictoriasDirtySecret, The FABRIC Act, and International Accord.</p>
