            <h3>OXFAM</h3>
            <br>
            <p>This global organization fights inequity and strives to end poverty and injustice. While this doesn't specifically relate to sustainable fashion, we all know that economic justice, gender equality, and climate action must be approached with an intersectional lens. Equal rights and equal treatment must be attained on all fronts in order for everyone to thrive. Some key campaigns include Secondhand September; 2000 Steps For Climate Justice; and Fight Injustice, Beat Poverty.</p>
