            <h3>Centre For Sustainable Fashion</h3>
            <br>
            <p>Sustainable fashion begins with design. The Centre For Sustainable Fashion is a university in London that is working from within to create change. Their curriculum questions and challenges the status quo and investigates existing systems within the fashion industry to transform it into one that recognizes ecological context and honors equity. Some ways in which they fight for sustainable fashion include research, knowledge exchange, policy advocacy, and of course, education.</p>
